<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_489" id="244r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l15"><expan>Ludw<ex>ig</ex></expan> vnd <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>G<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> cʒü <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l16">Gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als nehſten <expan>vvilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l17">
<add><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l18"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> beÿ <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l28">vnd Jr Jn <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew gevertigt habt des wir <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>dınſtlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_489_r1l29">vnd <expan>fleiſſıklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> / vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_489_line_1592246105163_277">er </ab></add> <expan>ſünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> redt / daʒ etlıch fürlewt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l19"> <expan>klagt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">J </del> ein Cʒollner pallen aufgeſniten het / vnd <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l20">begert / daʒ man der fürlewt einen cʒü ew ſchıckt / . Alſo ſchıcken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l21">wir dıſen <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertige<ex>n</ex></expan> fürman cʒü <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l23">daʒ Jr den <expan>gnediklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan> / vnd nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> vnd Jr das ervart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_r1l24"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darcʒü tün vvöllet / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> als Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_489_line_1576399737774_682">
<del rend="strikethrough">ewr gnad </del></ab></add> dann wol verſteet / . </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_489_line_1576399769422_711">
<del rend="strikethrough">Das <expan>wöll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </del> Als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_489" id="244r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ludw<ex>ig</ex></expan> und <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>g<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> czü <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als nehsten
                            <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendel, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell,
                                    <add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add> bey <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist <add>und ir in
                                    <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew gevertigt habt, des wir
                                    <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                <expan>dinstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                    <expan>fleissiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>danke<ex>n,</ex></expan></add> und <add>er</add>
<expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> redt, daz etlich fürlewt
                                <expan>klagt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ein czollner pallen aufgesniten
                        het und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad begert, daz man der fürlewt einen
                        czü ew schickt. Also schicken wir disen
                                <expan>gege<ex>n</ex>wertige<ex>n</ex></expan> fürman czü
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                        den <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan> und, nach <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> und ir
                        das ervart, <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darczü tün wöllet, als wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
